The quotations we are receiving from the Bordeaux market today startle us by their astronomic levels. We are ignoring them and are offering wines to you BASED ON OUR COST AND NOT ON REPLACEMENT VALUE.

It hardly requires an oracle to predict that the great Clarets listed below will command a substantially higher price a year hence. The reasons are obvious — fixed vineyard soil facing ever-increasing demand, world prosperity, continuous growth of interest in wine, the educational effects of jet travel, etc. NOW — not a year from now —IS THE RIGHT TIME 20 BUY.
